originalText.text: I met Stray at a boxing gym on the lower east side. During the pandemic, he began doing one-on-one, masked, outdoor private and group training sessions. I attended several private sessions with Jon and not only is he very flexible with his clients and their scheduling needs, he's a great coach. Regardless of your level, he ensures that you practice the basics and is very technical about how he teaches boxing. Highly recommend!

originalText.text: Stray boxing is excellent! Jon works with my son. He is an excellent teacher. He is passionate about his craft. He takes his time to make sure that the sessions are fun and educational. Jon wants everyone to excel not just at boxing but in life! I highly recommend Stay Boxing to anyone who wants to improve the quality of their well being.
